headline: Carnival Corporation & plc Completes Redemption of Remaining $322 Million 5.750% Senior Unsecured Notes due 2027
summary: Carnival Corporation & plc (NYSE/LSE: CCL; NYSE: CUK) today announced that Carnival Corporation (the "Company") has completed the redemption of the remaining outstanding principal amount (approximately $322 million) of its 5.750% senior unsecured notes due 2027.
